Redux- 

its a state management  library

Redux stores the state of your application.

1.Predictable state container for javascript apps

It’s for javascript  apps.

Its can be used with any js library or framework

Best use case is to pass data between unrelated components with our props drilling

_______________________________________________________


With redux , the state is stored outside the components, if any component want to use it, it communicates with state container

________________________________________________

React - UI library

Redux - is a state management library


We have react-redux package - offers connect react app with redux

React-redux is a package that binds react with redux

________________________________________

To create a redux project

Create a folder- rpm init —yes  (it creates a package.json file without promot)

npm install redux 

Create a index.js file and we are good to go
